name: Pot
description:
When you feel the vibe of detachment. Which transform the emotions into stable condition and detox thoughts of the brain. The pure vibe of the present with the joy of being alone touches the soul. 
NO fear, no sadness, no anxiety, no depression, no stress just calm and composed soul with healing and sensible focus. The concentration of yourself enhances growth and decision-making. You realize the aim of your life is joy and happiness, not materialistic things and money.
